---
title: Parmesan & Bacon Savoury Pancakes with Radish Salad & Dill-Parsley Drizzle | Serves 2
description: Craving pancakes but still want that savoury hit? We've got you covered with these cheesy bacon and herb pancakes drizzled
with a dill and parsley mayo, served with radish salad. We think there is no better way to start the day!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65d80703bb774993318aff22-50dd8e3a.jpeg
